            "concept_target": "[TRANSLATE]",
            "explanation_source": {
              "value": "To gently suggest something you and someone else could do, use 'We can' plus the base form of the verb. This sounds softer than 'Let's' — it offers a possibility instead of a direct push. After the verb, you can add an item using 'my' or 'your' to show whose it is.",
